          <td><a href="https://www.clivusmultrum.eu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Clivus Multrum</a> · <a href="https://good-design.org/projects/clivus-multrum-low-profile-cm-lp-waterless-composting-toilet-2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CM LP details</a></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Shower</strong></td>
          <td>Walk-in ~32&times;36", glass panel divider, 1.5 GPM low-flow head</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Vanity</strong></td>
          <td>Timber slab countertop, vessel basin, wall-mount brass faucet, open shelf below</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Door</strong></td>
          <td>Pocket door, centered on dividing wall</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Outdoor tub</strong></td>
          <td>Wood-fired or propane soaking tub on porch near bathroom end</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
